# TypeFlow Plugin Icon Placeholder

This file is a placeholder for the plugin icon.

## Requirements
- Format: PNG
- Recommended size: 128x128 pixels (or 256x256 for high-DPI)
- Background: Transparent or solid color
- Style: Should represent typography/fonts (e.g., letter "T", font icon, or typography-related symbol)

## Suggested Design
- A stylized "T" or "Tf" representing TypeFlow
- Clean, modern design that fits Framer's aesthetic
- Consider using a gradient or solid color that stands out in the plugin panel

## To Replace
Replace this placeholder with an actual icon.png file in the same directory.
The framer.json references this icon at "public/icon.png".
